text: Rosales, officially the Municipality of Rosales, (Pangasinan: Baley na Rosales; Ilokano: Ili ti Rosales; ), is a municipality in the province of Pangasinan, Philippines. According to the 2015 census, it has a population of 63,081 people. == References == Category:Settlements in the Philippines Category:Pangasinan
title: Rosales, Pangasinan
